"location":"Makkiyah"}},{"id":5720,"surah_id":79,"ayah":8,"page":583,"quarter_hizb":59,"juz":30,"manzil":7,"arabic":"قُلُوْبٌ يَّوْمَىِٕذٍ وَّاجِفَةٌۙ","kitabah":"قُلُوْبٌ يَّوْمَىِٕذٍ وَّاجِفَةٌۙ","latin":"Qulūbuy yauma'iżiw wājifah(tun).","arabic_words":["قُلُوْبٌ","يَّوْمَىِٕذٍ","وَّاجِفَةٌۙ"],"translation":"Hati manusia pada hari itu merasa sangat takut;","footnotes":null,"updated_at":null,"surah":{"id":79,"arabic":" النّٰزعٰت","latin":"An-Nāzi‘āt","transliteration":"An-Nazi‘at","translation":"Yang Mencabut Dengan Keras","num_ayah":46,"page":583,"location":"Makkiyah"}},{"id":5721,"surah_id":79,"ayah":9,"page":583,"quarter_hizb":59,"juz":30,"manzil":7,"arabic":"اَبْصَارُهَا خَاشِعَةٌ  ۘ","kitabah":"اَبْصَارُهَا خَاشِعَةٌ  ۘ","latin":"Abṣāruhā khāsyi‘ah(tun).","arabic_words":["اَبْصَارُهَا","خَاشِعَةٌ ۘ"],"translation":"pandangannya tertunduk.","footnotes":null,"updated_at":null,"surah":{"id":79,"arabic":" النّٰزعٰت","latin":"An-Nāzi‘āt","transliteration":"An-Nazi‘at","translation":"Yang Mencabut Dengan Keras","num_ayah":46,"page":583,"location":"Makkiyah"}},{"id":5722,"surah_id":79,"ayah":10,"page":583,"quarter_hizb":59,"juz":30,"manzil":7,"arabic":"يَقُوْلُوْنَ ءَاِنَّا لَمَرْدُوْدُوْنَ فِى الْحَافِرَةِۗ","kitabah":"يَقُوْلُوْنَ ءَاِنَّا لَمَرْدُوْدُوْنَ فِى الْحَافِرَةِۗ","latin":"Yaqūlūna a'innā lamardūdūna fil-ḥāfirah(ti).","arabic_words":["يَقُوْلُوْنَ","ءَاِنَّا","لَمَرْدُوْدُوْنَ","فِى","الْحَافِرَةِۗ"],"translation":"Mereka (di dunia) berkata, “Apakah kita benar-benar akan dikembalikan pada kehidupan yang semula?745)","footnotes":"745) Setelah orang-orang kafir mendengar berita tentang adanya hari Kebangkitan setelah mati, mereka merasa heran dan mengejek karena menurut keyakinan mereka, hari Kebangkitan itu tidak ada. Itulah sebabnya mereka berkata demikian.","updated_at":null,"surah":{"id":79,"arabic":" النّٰزعٰت","latin":"An-Nāzi‘āt","transliteration":"An-Nazi‘at","translation":"Yang Mencabut Dengan Keras","num_ayah":46,"page":583,"location":"Makkiyah"}},{"id":5723,"surah_id":79,"ayah":11,"page":583,"quarter_hizb":59,"juz":30,"manzil":7,"arabic":"ءَاِذَا كُنَّا عِظَامًا نَّخِرَةً ۗ","kitabah":"ءَاِذَا كُنَّا عِظَامًا نَّخِرَةً ۗ","latin":"A'iżā kunnā ‘iẓāman nakhirah(tan).","arabic_words":["ءَاِذَا","كُنَّا","عِظَامًا","نَّخِرَةً ۗ"],"translation":"Apabila kita telah menjadi tulang-belulang yang hancur, apakah kita (akan dibangkitkan juga)?”","footnotes":null,"updated_at":null,"surah":{"id":79,"arabic":" النّٰزعٰت","latin":"An-Nāzi‘āt","transliteration":"An-Nazi‘at","translation":"Yang Mencabut Dengan Keras","num_ayah":46,"page":583,"location":"Makkiyah"}},{"id":5724,"surah_id":79,"ayah":12,"page":583,"quarter_hizb":59,"juz":30,"manzil":7,"arabic":"قَالُوْا تِلْكَ اِذًا كَرَّةٌ خَاسِرَةٌ  ۘ","kitabah":"قَالُوْا تِلْكَ اِذًا كَرَّةٌ خَاسِرَةٌ  ۘ","latin":"Qālū tilka iżan karratun khāsirah(tun).","arabic_words":["قَالُوْا","تِلْكَ","اِذًا","كَرَّةٌ","خَاسِرَةٌ ۘ"],"translation":"Mereka berkata, “Kalau demikian, itu suatu pengembalian yang merugikan.”","footnotes":null,"updated_at":null,"surah":{"id":79,"arabic":" النّٰزعٰت","latin":"An-Nāzi‘āt","transliteration":"An-Nazi‘at","translation":"Yang Mencabut Dengan Keras","num_ayah":46,"page":583,"location":"Makkiyah"}},{"id":5725,"surah_id":79,"ayah":13,"page":583,"quarter_hizb":59,"juz":30,"manzil":7,"arabic":"فَاِنَّمَا هِيَ زَجْرَةٌ وَّاحِدَةٌۙ","kitabah":"فَاِنَّمَا هِيَ زَجْرَةٌ وَّاحِدَةٌۙ","latin":"Fa innamā hiya zajratuw wāḥidah(tun).","arabic_words":["فَاِنَّمَا","هِيَ","زَجْرَةٌ","وَّاحِدَةٌۙ"],"translation":"(Jangan dianggap sulit,) pengembalian itu (dilakukan) hanyalah dengan sekali tiupan.","footnotes":null,"updated_at":null,"surah":{"id":79,"arabic":" النّٰزعٰت","latin":"An-Nāzi‘āt","transliteration":"An-Nazi‘at","translation":"Yang Mencabut Dengan Keras","num_ayah":46,"page":583,"location":"Makkiyah"}},{"id":5726,"surah_id":79,"ayah":14,"page":583,"quarter_hizb":59,"juz":30,"manzil":7,"arabic":"فَاِذَا هُمْ بِالسَّاهِرَةِۗ","kitabah":"فَاِذَا هُمْ بِالسّ